Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.47,Normal,Moka,0000,0000,0000,,Tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:03.95,Normal,Tsukune,0000,0000,0000,,Em yêu ... yêu Tsukune-san!
